Connect to Server:
ssh ubuntu@server-ip

Generate SSH Key:
ssh-keygen

Copy Public Key:
ssh-copy-id ubuntu@server-ip

Secure Copy File:
scp file.txt ubuntu@server-ip:/tmp

Transfer Directory:
scp -r project ubuntu@server-ip:/opt

Real-Time Scenario:
Connect to AWS EC2.
ssh -i devops.pem ec2-user@public-ip
